These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, zinnia
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the person who growspoppy##8
3. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Flower   | zinnia | poppy | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, monopoly
1. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
2. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Game   | backgammon | monopoly | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
House: modern, farmhouse, townhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the modern house is not to the right of the townhouse house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| House   | farmhouse | modern | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, jet-ski
1. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |      3      |
| Transport   | jet-ski | tram | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, golf, cricket
1. the person who's sport is golf is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Sport   | climbing | golf | cricket |

